result.formatted_address: 34 Kam Lam St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: 百福餐廳小廚

reviews.text:
Bought fresh seafood from Mongkok market, and they cook the way we like. 
Very reasonable price and yummy!
Very cheap food.  Cooked fresh when order.  Typically can cook to your order of anything you can think of.
每次來旺角必吃！位在離地鐵比較遠的小巷裡，通常不用排隊，菜色很多種，早餐午餐晚餐都有！價格在市區裡算是非常平價，又好吃！大部分菜色都是老闆親手炒的，很有人情味的一家餐廳
